'''"Appreciated Reminiscences"''' was the [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]] translation of a popular [[Bith/Legends|Bith]] song which became [[Epoh Trebor]]'s theme song during his tours visiting the [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone troopers]] of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].

{{Music-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The title of this song is a reference to "[[Wikipedia:Thanks for the Memory|Thanks for the Memory]]," a song which was a trademark of [[Wikipedia:Bob Hope|Bob Hope]].

